[Game Rules for 2 players]
- The pile contains n chips, which can be arbitrarily defined at game setup;
- The first player removes any number of chips except to take the whole pile;
- Each person can remove one or more chips but not more than twice as many chips as the preceding player has taken;
- The player who removes the last chip wins!

[Game Mode]
- Default mode is user vs. computer, in which computer would take the optimal steps;
- 2 Player mode would be supported as well.
